### AI Interview Workflow Tests
### Use VS Code REST Client extension to run these tests

### 1. Start Interview
POST http://localhost:5678/webhook/start-interview
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe"
}

###

### 2. Submit First Answer
# Replace session_xxxxx with actual session_id from Step 1 response
POST http://localhost:5678/webhook/submit-answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "session_xxxxx",
  "answer": "I'm a frontend developer with 5 years of experience in React, Vue.js, and JavaScript. I've built numerous web applications and have strong skills in HTML, CSS, and modern JavaScript ES6+."
}

###

### 3. Submit Second Answer
